<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Percy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Percy,</orth> family name of the Earl of Northumberland: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 67</bibl>. His son Henry called so by eminence: <bibl n="shak. r2 2.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 21</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.6.11" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 6, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 53</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 1, 42</bibl> etc.
